title: Akane-chan (Little Miss Akane)
synopsis: A country girl, Akane was new to a prestigious school. She is full of vitality and everyone likes her. Hidemaro, the rich and arrogant boy likes her too. With everyone's help, she solves problems that come their way.
staff: [['Yamaguchi, Yasuo', ['Episode Director']], ['Nagaki, Bonjin', ['Episode Director']], ['Andou, Toyohiro', ['Script']], ['Yukimuro, Shunichi', ['Screenplay']]]
